<template>

</template>


<script>
import axios from 'axios'
export default{
  data(){
    return{
      name:'',
      email:''
    }
  },
  methods:{
    async fetchData(){
      try{
        response = await axios.get('http://localhost:5000/customer_dashboard', {headers:{
          Authorization:localStorage.getItem('authToken')
        }})
      }
      catch(error){
        if(error.response){
          alert('Something went wrong')
        }
      }
    }
  }
}


</script>


<style>

</style>
